Package: Spatialsmooth
Title: Spatial Transcriptomics Deconvolution Methods and Spatial smooth
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: person("njj", "yx", email = "njjyxl1006@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides functions to run various spatial transcriptomics deconvolution methods including CARD, RCTD, SPOTlight, SpatialDWLS,AdRoit,Seurat and Redeconve.
